Interface Expr

All Known Implementing Classes:
FilterExpr, IdExpr, LiteralExpr, MapExpr, OrderExpr, ReduceExpr, SortExpr, TruncateExpr
public interface Expr

Base interface of the expression AST, defining the eval method. Also defines a number of constants (enums) and inner classes for various kinds of expressions.
